description: Seeks to track the performance of the FTSE Emerging Markets All Cap China A Inclusion Index to the extent possible and before fees and expenses. Invests primarily in the U.S.-domiciled Vanguard FTSE Emerging Markets ETF. Employs a passively managed, index-sampling strategy to gain exposure to stocks included in the index. Low expenses minimize net tracking error.
name: Vanguard FTSE Emerging Markets All Cap Index ETF
